    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Children, when they become of age, will prize the parent who labored faithfully, and would not permit them to cherish wrong feelings or indulge in evil habits.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 7-13-1888\" data-link=\"820.8959\">The Signs of the Times, July 13, 1888</span>.</span></a></sup>",
