    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "When children have unbelieving parents, and their commands contradict the requirements of Christ, then, painful though it may be, they must obey God and trust the consequences with Him.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">6<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 11-15-1892\" data-link=\"821.12299\">The Review and Herald, November 15, 1892</span>.</span></a></sup>",
