    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Many Are Breaking the Fifth Commandment</strong>&mdash;In these last days children are so noted for their disobedience and disrespect that God has especially noticed it, and it constitutes a sign that the end is near. It shows that Satan has almost complete control of the minds of the young. By many, age is no more respected.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"1T 217.1\" data-link=\"116.1085\">Testimonies for the Church 1:217, 218</span>.</span></a></sup>",
