    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Children, it is necessary that your mothers love you, or else you would be very unhappy. And is it not also right that children love their parents, and show this love by pleasant looks, pleasant words, and cheerful, hearty cooperation, helping the father out-of-doors and the mother indoors?<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">12<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 129, 1898\" data-link=\"14063.5866001\">Manuscript 129, 1898</span>.</span></a></sup>",
